---
import PublicLayout from '../layouts/PublicLayout.astro';
---

<PublicLayout
  title="smagile Partner Network"
  description="Specialist contractor introduction service for UK insurers. Curated outside IR35 agile, product, and delivery professionals."
>
  <section class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 py-16 sm:py-20">
    <h1 class="text-3xl sm:text-4xl font-bold text-grey-900 dark:text-white">
      smagile Partner Network
    </h1>
    <p class="mt-2 text-lg text-accent dark:text-accent-light font-medium">
      Collaboration beats coordination.
    </p>

    <div class="mt-8 prose prose-lg dark:prose-invert max-w-none">
      <p class="text-xl text-grey-700 dark:text-warm-200">
        smagile Partner Network is a specialist contractor introduction service focused
        exclusively on the UK insurance sector.
      </p>

      <p>
        We introduce a small, curated network of outside IR35 agile, product, and delivery
        contractors to insurers running complex change and transformation initiatives.
      </p>

      <p>
        The Partner Network exists to help UK insurers reduce delivery risk by introducing
        contractors we trust. These are people we have worked with directly on insurance
        and regulated change programmes, or would confidently hire ourselves.
      </p>

      <p>
        This is not recruitment and it is not volume based. We do not forward CVs or run
        keyword searches. We make targeted introductions based on real delivery capability
        and sector experience.
      </p>

      <h2>What we do</h2>
      <ul>
        <li>Outside IR35 contractor introductions only</li>
        <li>Agile, product, and delivery specialists</li>
        <li>UK insurance experience required</li>
        <li>Practitioner-led assessment</li>
      </ul>

      <h2>What we do not do</h2>
      <ul>
        <li>Permanent recruitment</li>
        <li>Inside IR35 placements</li>
        <li>High volume agency recruitment</li>
      </ul>

      <h2>Roles we cover</h2>
      <p>
        Ranging through strategy setting, design, delivery, and validation: UI/UX designers,
        developers, testers, architects, business and process analysts, Scrum Masters, Agile
        Coaches, Delivery Managers, Product Owners, Product Managers, and other senior
        delivery leaders.
      </p>

      <h2>For contractors</h2>
      <p>
        If you are an independent agile, product, or delivery professional with UK insurance
        experience and our values resonate with you, we would love to hear from you.
      </p>

      <div class="mt-8 not-prose">
        <a
          href="/contact/"
          class="inline-block px-8 py-3.5 bg-primary hover:bg-primary-dark text-white font-medium rounded-lg transition-all shadow-lg shadow-primary/20 hover:shadow-primary/30 hover:-translate-y-0.5"
        >
          Start a conversation
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</PublicLayout>
